This repository currently contains original shader approximations shaped after
well-known open algorithms. Exact third-party shader ports must preserve
upstream headers and add per-file attribution here before import.

Planned attributions before exact shader integration:

- AMD FidelityFX Super Resolution 1.0 EASU + RCAS, MIT.
- AMD Contrast Adaptive Sharpening, MIT.
- Anime4K v4 from bloc97/Anime4K, MIT.
- ArtCNN from Artoriuz/ArtCNN, MIT pending verification at import.
- RAVU shader variants from the mpv-player shaders ecosystem, LGPL-3.0.
